## Local Development

### Prerequisites

- Java {{JAVA_VERSION}}
- Maven 3.9+
- Docker + Docker Compose

### Start Services

```bash
docker compose up -d
```

| Service | Address | Credentials |
|---------|---------|-------------|
{{#if DB}}| PostgreSQL | `localhost:5432` | `app` / `app` |
{{/if}}{{#if MESSAGING}}| RabbitMQ Management | http://localhost:15672 | `app` / `app` |
{{/if}}{{#if AUTH}}| Keycloak Admin | http://localhost:8180 | `admin` / `admin` |
{{/if}}| Application | http://localhost:{{APP_PORT}} | – |

### Build and Start Application

```bash
# Build
./mvnw clean package -DskipTests

# Start (locally, outside Docker)
./mvnw {{FRAMEWORK_RUN_COMMAND}}
```

### Health Check

```bash
curl http://localhost:{{APP_PORT}}/{{HEALTH_ENDPOINT}}
```

### Run Tests

```bash
# All tests
