## Architecture

The project follows the **BCE pattern** (Boundary / Control / Entity):

```
src/main/java/{{PACKAGE_PATH}}/
├── boundary/
│   ├── rest/          # REST endpoints
{{#if MESSAGING}}│   └── messaging/     # Messaging consumers / producers
{{/if}}├── control/           # Business logic (services)
└── entity/            # JPA entities, repositories, DTOs
```

Architecture rules are checked at build time by **Taikai** (ArchUnit):

```bash
./mvnw test -Dtest=ArchitectureTest
```

### Database Migrations

Migrations are managed by **Flyway**:

```
src/main/resources/db/migration/
├── V1__initial_schema.sql
└── V2__...
```

No `ddl-auto=create` – all schema changes via Flyway scripts.

